@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@
+# ADR 0004 — Dependency-free static prototype
+
+**Status:** Accepted for this repository stage
+
+## Decision
+
+Implement the concept as deterministic HTML, CSS, JavaScript, SVG, and structured demo data with no runtime package dependencies.
+
+## Rationale
+
+The current objective is to validate product architecture, information hierarchy, interactions, responsive behavior, and implementation contracts before selecting production services and frameworks.
+
+## Consequences
+
+- the prototype is portable and easy to inspect
+- interactions are illustrative and do not persist
+- authentication, APIs, integrations, and legal engines remain specified rather than simulated as production-ready
+- migration into a production stack remains a deliberate next step
